/test_q4_0_dot.py && python3 tests/test_q4_0_dequant.py && python3 tests/test_q4_0_q8_0_dot_kernel.py passed |\n| 2026-04-16 | loop-077 | IQ-097 Q8_0 checked matrix wrapper compat | done | Added `Q8_0_DotRowsQ16MatrixVectorChecked` alias in `src/quant/q8_0_dot.HC` with parity test in `tests/test_q8_0_dot.py`; `python3 tests/test_q8_0_dot.py && python3 tests/test_q8_0_dot_matrix_vector.py` passed |\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
